      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting with my trusty car and it\u2019s ready for its next big adventure! It\u2019s been super well-maintained and runs like a dream, making it a perfect pick if you're looking for something reliable and ready to hit the road. It\u2019s in great shape and has plenty of life left in it. Feel free to reach out\u2014I\u2019d love to see it go to a great home!",
