    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a well-sorted E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. This example is equipped with a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and the M Variable Differential Lock, providing exceptional mechanical feedback and traction. The chassis integrity is excellent, with the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) offering distinct profiles for various road conditions. Crucially, the rod bearings and throttle actuators\u2014essential preventative maintenance items for this platform\u2014have been addressed. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited driving, the overall aerodynamic profile and Alpine White finish remain sharp. A mechanically sound driver's car for the purist seeking the final naturally aspirated M-car experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
