      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and presents beautifully. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish with only the slightest signs of careful use, while the interior is remarkably clean, featuring well-preserved upholstery and a fully operational suite of electronics. Under the hood, the car is mechanically sound, having undergone regular servicing with all fluids and filters recently addressed. It delivers a smooth, quiet ride with responsive handling and firm braking. This is a turn-key example for a discerning buyer who values a documented service history and a car that has clearly been a point of pride for its owner. Clean title in hand and ready for its next chapter.",
